993
01:25:21,200 --> 01:25:24,540
- Ourselves?  - That's right.

994
01:25:24,540 --> 01:25:28,370
Tomorrow night, right after we return our guest.

995
01:25:29,810 --> 01:25:32,540
- I can't.  - You must.

996
01:25:34,420 --> 01:25:38,820
Remember: Share and share alike.

997
01:25:38,820 --> 01:25:42,920
You stop it! Stop it!

998
01:25:47,000 --> 01:25:49,870
- Decide on something?  - That'll be fine.

999
01:25:49,870 --> 01:25:52,000
I'll have it wrapped.

1000
01:25:52,000 --> 01:25:55,740
But it was more than that, much more than that...

1001
01:25:55,740 --> 01:25:59,780
