1005
01:26:09,580 --> 01:26:13,760
and no more than that can be asked of mortal man on this earth.

1006
01:26:13,760 --> 01:26:16,630
You loved your wife dearly.

1007
01:26:16,630 --> 01:26:19,700
You bestowed upon your dear mother and father...

1008
01:26:19,700 --> 01:26:23,430
all the care, all the attention,

1009
01:26:23,430 --> 01:26:28,190
patience and comfort that they needed... in the sunset of their lives.

1010
01:26:28,970 --> 01:26:31,510
And those of us who are left behind...

1011
01:26:31,510 --> 01:26:34,040
to grieve for you, Joseph,

1012
01:26:34,040 --> 01:26:38,010
can only bow to the divine judgement of our Lord,

1013
01:26:38,010 --> 01:26:41,620
who has chosen to take you away from us...

1014
01:26:41,620 --> 01:26:45,220
in this cruel accident.

1015
01:26:45,220 --> 01:26:48,820
Oh, how great the holiness of our God.

1016
01:26:48,820 --> 01:26:51,790
For He knoweth all things.

1017
01:26:51,790 --> 01:26:55,600
