1027
01:27:40,440 --> 01:27:43,150
and messing in things that were none of your business.

1028
01:27:43,150 --> 01:27:45,750
Now go away. Please!

1029
01:27:45,750 --> 01:27:48,250
- Mrs. Maloney, I have to talk to you.  - He's dead and buried.

1030
01:27:48,250 --> 01:27:50,390
