1045
01:28:46,980 --> 01:28:51,670
Now go away, and don't ever come near me again.

1046
01:28:54,850 --> 01:28:58,580
Fake! Fake!

1047
01:29:11,730 --> 01:29:14,770
Wait a second, now. You're the one that's exaggerating.

1048
01:29:14,770 --> 01:29:18,510
