1168
01:38:44,640 --> 01:38:47,240
What are we going to do?

1169
01:38:47,240 --> 01:38:49,610
Nothing!

1170
01:38:49,610 --> 01:38:52,010
Until later tonight.

1171
01:39:04,290 --> 01:39:07,130
