1178
01:40:49,100 --> 01:40:51,430
Good evening, honey.

1179
01:40:51,430 --> 01:40:55,270
Madame Blanche, I wonder if I might suggest to you to remove your car from our driveway.

1180
01:40:55,270 --> 01:40:58,240
