1211
01:43:15,880 --> 01:43:18,740
It looks like Miss Tyler needs some rest.

1212
01:43:23,820 --> 01:43:26,620
Will you do as I say?

1213
01:43:43,170 --> 01:43:47,400
No. No.

1214
01:44:29,080 --> 01:44:31,520
Unlock the door.

1215
01:44:38,960 --> 01:44:40,960
Cheer up, Fran.

1216
01:44:40,960 --> 01:44:44,290
Let's go get the new diamond for our chandelier.

1217
01:45:08,060 --> 01:45:12,120
Wow. It's gorgeous.

1218
01:45:22,170 --> 01:45:25,140
And now for Madame Blanche.

1219
01:50:45,960 --> 01:50:48,450
Oh, my God.

1220
01:51:32,310 --> 01:51:34,740
Blanche?

1221
01:51:45,690 --> 01:51:48,120
Blanche?

1222
01:51:55,130 --> 01:51:57,560
Blanche?

1223
01:52:26,860 --> 01:52:31,030
If I'm talking too much, perhaps it's because you're not talking.

1224
01:52:31,030 --> 01:52:34,330
It's my stomach, Arthur. Murder doesn't agree with it.

1225
01:52:34,330 --> 01:52:36,970
You think I'm looking forward to it?

1226
01:52:36,970 --> 01:52:40,800
If Joe Maloney had been more efficient, they'd both be dead by now.

1227
01:52:41,680 --> 01:52:44,340
You can have my share, Arthur.

1228
01:52:44,340 --> 01:52:49,210
You can keep both diamonds all to yourself if you'll just end it.

1229
01:52:49,850 --> 01:52:52,650
I'll tell you what I'll do.

1230
01:52:52,650 --> 01:52:55,820
If you help me carry Sleeping Beauty up out of the cellar, load her into our car...

1231
01:52:55,820 --> 01:53:00,060
and drive her out to some deserted road where a suicide can take place,

1232
01:53:00,060 --> 01:53:02,890
I promise you we'll talk this thing over.

1233
01:53:03,630 --> 01:53:06,700
- Okay?  - What about the cab driver?

1234
01:53:06,700 --> 01:53:11,070
If she was able to find us, I'm sure he can too.

1235
01:53:11,070 --> 01:53:15,840
- He'll walk right into our hands.  - Your hands, not mine.

1236
01:53:15,840 --> 01:53:18,350
Don't you think we ought to go down and take a look at her?

1237
01:53:18,350 --> 01:53:20,510
It's been a while since we gave her that shot.

1238
01:53:20,510 --> 01:53:24,280
- You do it.  - Okay.

1239
01:54:37,690 --> 01:54:40,960
You'll be happy to know she's still unconscious.

1240
01:55:03,020 --> 01:55:06,080
- Blanche.  - Shh!

1241
01:55:31,140 --> 01:55:37,620
I'll put this end into her exhaust pipe... and the other end in the window.

1242
01:55:37,620 --> 01:55:40,780
That way, it'll look like suicide.

1243
01:56:15,020 --> 01:56:17,260
Better go and get her now.

1244
01:56:17,260 --> 01:56:20,780
I'll take her in our car. You follow in hers.

1245
01:56:33,640 --> 01:56:36,070
You take hold of her feet.

1246
01:56:40,550 --> 01:56:43,950
Jesus, she's heavy.

1247
01:56:45,120 --> 01:56:47,550
George!

1248
01:56:48,620 --> 01:56:51,390
Got 'em.

1249
01:56:54,390 --> 01:56:56,900
Blanche, you faked that one beautifully.

1250
01:56:56,900 --> 01:56:59,870
You are still the champ.

1251
01:56:59,870 --> 01:57:02,440
Thank you, George.

1252
01:57:02,440 --> 01:57:06,060
Do you realize how much the reward is for those two?

1253
01:57:07,510 --> 01:57:09,540
Yes.

1254
01:57:09,540 --> 01:57:12,230
But do you realize how much more the reward would be...

1255
01:57:13,020 --> 01:57:16,190
if we could find the diamonds and turn 'em in?

1256
01:57:22,460 --> 01:57:25,290
What's the matter with you?

1257
01:57:25,290 --> 01:57:27,460
I...

1258
01:57:27,460 --> 01:57:29,890
Blanche, what's the matter?

1259
01:57:40,610 --> 01:57:43,080
Blanche, what's the matter?

1260
01:57:56,590 --> 01:57:59,020
What is it?

1261
01:58:29,060 --> 01:58:31,590
Blanche, you did it!

1262
01:58:31,590 --> 01:58:34,030
You are psychic!

1263
01:58:35,900 --> 01:58:38,730
- What am I doing here on the stairs?  - You're not a fake.

1264
01:58:38,730 --> 01:58:41,430
You actually found one. Look.

1265
01:58:41,430 --> 01:58:43,440
I did?

1266
01:58:43,440 --> 01:58:46,410
I'll get the police on the phone and give them our good news,

1267
01:58:46,410 --> 01:58:50,070
and call Miss Rainbird and give her the bad.

1268
01:58:56,880 --> 01:58:59,820
Operator, can I have the police?


